        "# üîê Password Strength Checker\n",
        "\n",
        "A simple tool to check the strength of a password in **Python**.\n",
        "It scores a password based on **length, character diversity, common patterns, and repetitions**,\n",
        "and provides suggestions to make the password stronger.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## üöÄ Features\n",
        "- ‚úÖ Scores password strength from **0‚Äì100**\n",
        "- ‚úÖ Labels: *Very Weak, Weak, Fair, Strong, Excellent*\n",
        "- ‚úÖ Detects common weak passwords (e.g., `123456`, `password`)\n",
        "- ‚úÖ Checks for repeated characters (like `aaa`)\n",
        "- ‚úÖ Provides suggestions for improvement\n",
        "- ‚úÖ Optional **Flask API** to use in web apps\n",
        "\n",
